Paper: hep-th/0002208

Date: 2000-02-24

Title: Thermal Quantum Fields in Static Electromagnetic Backgrounds

Authors: A.A. Actor and K.D. Rothe

Comments: 22 pages

Journal-ref: J.Phys. A33 (2000) 4585-4598

We present and discuss, at a general level, new mathematical results on thespatial nonuniformity of thermal quantum fields coupled minimally to staticbackground electromagnetic potentials. Two distinct examples are worked throughmagnetic fields coupled to a thermal quantum scalar field.